ee.ria.dhx.types

Class DhxPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ee.ria.dhx.types.DhxPackage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IncomingDhxPackage, OutgoingDhxPackage

    public abstract class DhxPackage
extends java.lang.Object
    DHX package object. Contains information needed for sending the document and for receiving the document. Cannot be instantiated by itself. Eiteher outgoing or incoming package must be instantiated
    Author:
    Aleksei Kokarev
